    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. the problem is that these specific groups... they aren't just hackers. they're intelligence professionals. they know how to look past standard VPNs and common encryption. they anticipate the usual privacy moves. if i use crypto or a vpn, won't they just see that as a sign that i'm hiding something and follow the pattern? how do i actually blend in so they think i'm just another normal person with no history?",
